title: Modifying the Sidebar
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

The [[Sidebar|$:/core/ui/PageTemplate/sidebar]] consists of several sections that are really [[transcluded|Transclusion]] tiddlers. You can easily add, remove and reorder the sections.

! Adding a Sidebar Section

# Create a tiddler with the desired content
# Give it the tag ''~$:/tags/SideBarSection''

! Removing a Sidebar Section

# Access the sections tiddler. If you don't know the title of the relevant tiddler, you can create a temporary tiddler with the text `<<tag $:/tags/SideBarSection>>`. From the resulting tag dropdown, select the section tiddler.
# In edit mode for the section tiddler, remove the tag `$:/tags/SideBarSection` and save

! Reordering Sidebar Sections

# Open [[$:/tags/SideBarSection]]
# Reorder the titles in `list` field and  save

! See also

*[[How to Add a New Tab to the Sidebar]]
